This project focuses on developing a digital hotel management system for resorts using React.js, a popular JavaScript hotel for building user interfaces. The system aims to enhance the organization, accessibility, and usability of digital resources such as e-rooms within the resorts. By leveraging React.js, the project aims to create dynamic and interactive user interfaces, providing customers with a seamless browsing experience. Additionally, the project explores the integration of React.js with backend technologies to enable features such as user authentication, search functionality, and personalized recommendations. Through the use of React.js, this project aims to deliver a modern and responsive digital hotel management system tailored for college needs.
